relation: New Jersey Second Amendment Society A local group of New Jersey residents.

Second Amendment Women Shooting Club/SAW We are women safeguarding our Second Amendment Rights, through activism and education. Founded by Shari Spivack and Sandra Muldoon, NRA certified firearms instructors, the club is dedicated to teaching and providing continuing opportunities for women to enjoy shooting. SAW now is offering various levels of training classes for women only at our home range; the Woodland Park Range in New Jersey.
